{"tid":2234530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中信海直」旗下三架直升機參與把12香港人送中與新屋嶺輪姦案","createTime":"2020-10-08T03:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T05:57:04.000Z","uid":26770,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e231da914b901186dcec7503caffd841aaeaef52","tid":2234530,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:35:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2234293/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2234293/page/1</a><br />\n請睇埋<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sVARkir.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsVARkir.jpg&h=d6790b05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係共產黨手下的重要KEEPER,掌握國家命脈<br />\n<br />\n<ins>范鴻齡</ins>明明無相關履歷撈到HA一哥係因為條友係中信系前大佬, <br />\n做到呢D位一定係<ins>同689差不多級別的地下黨員</ins><br />\n<br />\n<strong>咩迫政府封關唔導致立即要清算HA人,講真封唔封好撚閒<br />\n<span class=\"red\">而係HA人爆出香港警魔輪姦示威者</span><br />\n<br />\n係荃灣警輪姦案時, 狗隊高層曾要求傳媒高層幫幫手壓CASE<br />\n因為大量傳媒唔配合所以港共攪認可媒體制度係報復</strong>"},{"pid":"1eb705ca220f0aa3671454d422229ad1cbbddfaa","tid":2234530,"uid":26770,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"N件重大輪姦案係美國政界影響好大<br />\n<br />\n特別奶共法院簽搜查令迫害受害人葬送左香港奶共法院<br />\n係公民黨/大律師公會幫手COOL DOWN先未死"},{"pid":"4a6a376ba467eee05ea886439f844c9dd887d5d8","tid":2234530,"uid":26770,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:40:53.000Z","msg":"中信系旗下的某些行業<br />\n你唔係自己友就算係香港李首富都無份參與<br />\n<br />\n姐係KOL成日講的敏感行業"},{"pid":"676c0fb10da431288203ad644ddc298bb15234fa","tid":2234530,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T03:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765e5ae3269d97072a56be97c8bc6bd916182bb3","tid":2234530,"uid":3241